{
  "stem": "7455.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My brother told everybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They stayed in a one-story building where the one window was to the back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And it was on a second floor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "No fire escapes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So they were not guarding that place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So they took sheets and tied it into ropes, and let themselves down.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "My two brothers went down at first, and then the others.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That in the morning, they're going to liquidate that-- that camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They-- they are moving on, and they don't need any more that road work for them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My brothers started to run as they let themselves down, and the others are to follow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But as they were running, they heard shots, which means they were discovered.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "My brother-- my brothers ran and wound up in a bombed out building and a cellar under the rubble, and they stayed there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Later-- but they stayed there for several days, and later they were hungry.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They had to go look for places.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we knew that we have a-- a fellow, Janic Kowalski, that we knew.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they figure at night, they're going to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Maybe he'll give them some bread or something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He's a good man.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He's not going to point them out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they begged he should give them a few days-- shelter for a few days.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And then they're going to look for another place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "It was endangering him, but there were some kind people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And my brothers stayed there a few days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they were-- they knew that I am at Pawluks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said, is she alive?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They knew that they-- they are liquidating the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he was kind enough to go to the Pawluks and find out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Pawluks told him that they sent me away, and that I am near Tarnopol in a place.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
